Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:05.35,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I still remember you;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:07.81,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The time we shared,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:10.39,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The love you gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:15.36,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Though everything has changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:20.07,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You push me to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:29.91,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海よりも深い奥底から見守っている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:35.50,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别かれた未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:43.13,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I still love you, even though I miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:52.06,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永久に続く悲しみの夜の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.06,0:22:56.90,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛は生きる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:02.57,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I will be here for you, always and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:08.83,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今もずっと願っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:19.80,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温かいこの闇の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:05.35,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我依然記得你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:07.81,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}記得我們共度的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:10.39,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}記得你給予我的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:15.36,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}儘管一切都已面目全非
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:20.07,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你仍是我活著的動力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:29.91,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自比海更深的幽穴深底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:35.50,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}守護著各自分歧的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:43.13,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我依然愛著你  即使我只能思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:52.06,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在通向永恆的哀慟深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.06,0:22:56.90,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}猶自有愛存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:02.57,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會為你守在這裡  始終如一  直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:08.83,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我仍將繼續為你祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:19.80,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這溫暖的黑暗之中
